[thinking] **Considering code annotations and tests**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking that we ought to include type annotations for all functions and most variables, similar to how Java does it. For the top-level test classes, I agree they should be public. Also, in Java, it makes sense to use imports rather than qualified names. I wonder if I need to read upstream tests, but maybe it’s not necessary. It might help to look at the FreemarkerServlet tests, though it seems we need to confirm some parameters.
